## **What is an AI Voice Agent?**

An **AI voice agent** is a conversational tool powered by artificial intelligence that facilitates voice-based interactions. Using speech recognition and machine learning algorithms, these agents can process natural language, understand user intent, and deliver accurate, context-aware responses.

**AI voice agents** can handle various tasks, from customer support and appointment scheduling to more complex operations like real-time data analysis. Their ability to learn and adapt makes them an essential tool for businesses seeking efficiency and innovation.
